citations:
    citation-agot-bran-ii:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Bran II"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Bran. On the day of departure, Bran climbs the First Keep and discovers Jaime and Cersei Lannister engaged in an incestuous encounter. They discover him hanging from the window ledge. Jaime says 'The things I do for love' and pushes Bran from the window. Bran falls into the courtyard below."
